     The[0m[2m problem is that between[0m[2m checking `job["[0m[2mstatus"] == "[0m[2mpending"` and setting[0m[2m `job["status[0m[2m"] = "processing[0m[2m"`, there's[0m[2m an `await asyncio[0m[2m.sleep(0.[0m[2m01)`. During[0m[2m this sleep, other[0m[2m workers can also check[0m[2m the same job,[0m[2m see it as "[0m[2mpending", and then[0m[2m all of[0m[2m them will set it[0m[2m to "processing"[0m[2m and return[0m[2m it.
     
